# Stack Baseline

Use pnpm, TypeScript strict, TanStack Start/Router, React, shadcn/ui + Tailwind,
SurrealDB, Dexie IndexedDB saves, Vitest, Playwright, Biome, Docker, and Dokploy.
No npm/yarn, ESLint, Prettier, Redux, Zustand, real club/player names, or localStorage saves.
